                    <ab>Quęrela <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Martinua">Martini</name></persName> et alterius
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> ac
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName> fratrum
                        et <persName><name ref="Bona">Bonę</name></persName> horum sorore, coram
                        nobilibus viris et infrascripto <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs>, contra
                            <persName key="#Specialized_workers"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrandum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">aurificem</rs> filium Dominici, qui debebat
                        prędictis <rs key="#Price">libras 8 denariorum Venetorum</rs> pro <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">duabus petiis terrę</rs>, positis in
                            <placeName key="#Venditio #Landed_possessions #Price"
                            >Raviola</placeName> prope <placeName ref="#places/4683"
                            >Bretaliam</placeName>, <rs key="#Venditio">venditis</rs> eidem
                        Ildebrando. Actum <placeName ref="#places/7">Bononię</placeName>, rog.
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName>
                        notarii, 1054, imperatore domino Henrico filio quondam Conradi imperatoris
                        VIII, 6 martii, indictione VII.</ab>
                </div>
